,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:10:10.000Z","msg":"去到英國冇人會搞你 <br />\n<br />\n完<span class=\"large\"></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:32:14.000Z","msg":"有冇英國高層執法人員一定會回覆同可以直接聯絡唔該比個我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3daa0cb06e097ac3b7a4b8258a10a4b6d5ccf563","tid":2508591,"uid":251696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d611d3365d6ecbe197b742069b4e8fa973d1bc6","tid":2508591,"uid":288941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8fc41765038af1d48da55ebd3ef8bb8739e3eebe","tid":2508591,"uid":282438,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T01:43:45.000Z","msg":"睇左3次<br />\n仲要轉MK MODE先睇得明<br />\n<br />\n懶人包 ：<br />\n唔好以為去左外國就無事<br />\n佢哋會用當人黑社會攪你<br />\n<br />\nPR玩到無野好玩啊，又吹奏移民唔好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T09:44:18.000Z","msg":"你睇得明 真係好勁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:35:55.000Z","msg":"PR都要有資格先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你覺得我有呢個背景實在太高，而家我出文好大機會都係製造我係打手啫，但我出文意思係我要搵英國真正公開有權力嘅機構幫手而唔係吹風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而有人可以令到我係度出文，啫係我已經被玩左好多鑊，而對方亦係英國人身份"},{"pid":"c2c4ef31ea17d56984163c9486b731d2752199bf","tid":2508591,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-29T10:35:57.000Z","msg":"以為係我中文唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/ohno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}